诺曼尼说她“压抑”了一些在《第五和谐》中的记忆https://www.nme.com/news/music/normani-says-shes-suppressed-some-memories-from-being-in-fifth-harmony-3763113?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=normani-says-shes-因五和声而被压抑的一些记忆Surej SinghThu, 06 Jun 2024 06:55:18 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3763113 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/normani@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="《名利场》中的 Normani x Saint Laurent x NBCUniversal“奥本海默”电影祝酒" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/normani@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/normani@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/normani@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/normani@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/normani@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/normani@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我只记得事情并不全是坏事”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/normani-says-shes-suppressed-some-memories-from-being-in-fifth-harmony-3763113">诺曼尼称她“压抑”了一些在第五和声中的记忆，该</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/normani@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="《名利场》中的 Normani x Saint Laurent x NBCUniversal“奥本海默”电影祝酒" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/normani@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/normani@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/normani@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/normani@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/normani@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/normani@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/normani">诺曼尼</a>透露，她“压抑”了与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fifth-harmony">Fifth Harmony</a>合作时的一些记忆 - 看看下面这位歌手是怎么说的。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong> <a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/noughties-pop-references-normanis-incredible-motivation-video-2539007">诺曼尼令人难以置信的“动机”视频中所有 00 年代流行音乐的点头</a></li></ul><p>在<a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-features/normani-dopamine-janet-jackson-brandy-fifth-harmony-interview-1235033005/?sub_action=logged_in" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《滚石》杂志</em>的最新采访</a>中，这位前 Fifth Harmony 成员谈到了她在这个流行乐队中的时光，以及自 2018 年五人乐队解散以来她是如何应对的。</p><p>当被问及单飞后她的成长情况时，诺曼尼回答说，她对一切都“感激”，甚至是“那些我可能感到不足或不足的时刻。”这肯定与我为何成为现在的样子有很大关系。这确实对我的信心造成了打击。”</p><p>在 Fifth Harmony 任职期间，诺曼尼多次遭遇唱片公司高管甚至乐队粉丝的种族歧视，他们认为她不如乐队中的同行，并在乐队发行的专辑中将她降级为比她的队友小得多的角色。 </p><figure id="attachment_3750992" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3750992" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3750992" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/normani@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/normani@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/normani@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/normani@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/normani@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/normani@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/normani@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3750992" class="wp-caption-text">诺曼尼。图片来源：Gilbert Flores/Variety via Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>回顾她过去在乐队中的挣扎，诺曼尼透露：“我们是如此天真，我认为这就是我们在非常不现实的情况下不得不面对现实的挣扎。我总是说我们已经尽力了，所以我感到自豪。”</p><p>她接着补充道：“有太多事情我什至不记得了，因为我压抑了它。这只是我保护自己免于处理所有事情的方法。但我记得的是，这并不全是坏事。是的，我们很挣扎，但我们共同取得的成就也非常美好。”</p><p>在谈到她即将推出的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/normani-announces-debut-solo-album-3590974">备受期待的首张专辑《Dopamine》</a>时，诺曼尼透露，她希望粉丝们发现她“尽管我经历了一切，但她仍然很坚强。”这证明了我的力量、韧性和纪律。” </p><figure id="attachment_3592051" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3592051" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3592051" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/normani-Katie-Jones_Variety-via-Getty-Images.jpg" alt="诺曼尼在圣丹斯电影节综艺和金球奖派对上。图片来源：凯蒂·琼斯/Variety via Getty Images" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/normani-Katie-Jones_Variety-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/normani-Katie-Jones_Variety-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/normani-Katie-Jones_Variety-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/normani-Katie-Jones_Variety-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/normani-Katie-Jones_Variety-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/normani-Katie-Jones_Variety-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3592051" class="wp-caption-text">诺曼尼在圣丹斯电影节综艺和金球奖派对上。图片来源：凯蒂·琼斯/Variety via Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>四月，诺曼尼<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/normanis-debut-album-finally-has-a-release-date-3750991">终于透露了《多巴胺》的上映日期</a>。她自单飞以来的首张歌曲集《Dopamine》将于 6 月 14 日通过 RCA Records 发行。<a href="https://www.wheresthedamnalbum.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">您可以在此处预先保存相册</a>。</p><p>这一消息是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/normani-new-music-on-the-way-album-singles-sundance-3574016">在她一月份调侃这张唱片后宣布的，称它“确实是她创作过的最好的音乐”。</a>当月晚些时候，诺曼尼进一步谈到了即将发行的唱片，将其描述为“[她的]进化的代表”。 “对我来说，这张即将发行的专辑不仅仅是音乐的问世，”她说。 “这感觉就像是我为了这一刻所经历的一切的代表。这张专辑给人一种解放的感觉，就像一个自由的季节。不仅因为这张唱片终于面世了，还因为这是对一切的庆祝。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/normani-says-shes-suppressed-some-memories-from-being-in-fifth-harmony-3763113">诺曼尼称她“压抑”了一些在第五和声中的记忆，该</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
雷丁和利兹正在赠送门票以鼓励年轻人投票https://www.nme.com/news/music/reading-leeds-are-giving-away-tickets-to-encourage-young-people-to-vote-3763107?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=reading-leeds-正在赠送门票以鼓励年轻人投票Tom SkinnerThu, 06 Jun 2024 06:44:17 +0000 Music NewsNewsPoliticsDanceElectronicHip-hopIndiePopPop-PunkRapRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3763107 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/BiffyClyro_NMEReading21_AFord-4805.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Biffy Clyro 在 2021 年阅读节上亮相时的主舞台。图片来源：Andy Ford for NME" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/BiffyClyro_NMEReading21_AFord-4805.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/BiffyClyro_NMEReading21_AFord-4805-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/BiffyClyro_NMEReading21_AFord-4805-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/BiffyClyro_NMEReading21_AFord-4805-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/BiffyClyro_NMEReading21_AFord-4805-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/BiffyClyro_NMEReading21_AFord-4805-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>格拉斯顿伯里还参与了新的“Just Vote”活动</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/reading-leeds-are-giving-away-tickets-to-encourage-young-people-to-vote-3763107">雷丁和利兹联队赠送门票以鼓励年轻人投票的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/BiffyClyro_NMEReading21_AFord-4805.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Biffy Clyro 在 2021 年阅读节上亮相时的主舞台。图片来源：Andy Ford for NME" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/BiffyClyro_NMEReading21_AFord-4805.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/BiffyClyro_NMEReading21_AFord-4805-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/BiffyClyro_NMEReading21_AFord-4805-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/BiffyClyro_NMEReading21_AFord-4805-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/BiffyClyro_NMEReading21_AFord-4805-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/BiffyClyro_NMEReading21_AFord-4805-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/reading-leeds-festival-2024">雷丁和利兹</a>将赠送今年节日的免费门票，以鼓励年轻人在<a href="https://www.nme.com/politics/uk-set-for-surprise-snap-uk-general-election-this-summer-rishi-sunak-3758594">英国大选</a>中投票。查找下面的所有详细信息。</p><p>这场双场地活动将于 8 月 23 日至 25 日期间举行，其中<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lana-del-rey">Lana Del Rey</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/liam-gallagher">Liam Gallagher</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/catfish-and-the-bottlemen">Catfish &amp; The Bottlemen</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blink-182">Blink-182</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fred-again">Fred Again..</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gerry-cinnamon">Gerry Cinnamon</a>均名列前茅。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/reading-festival-2023-best-moments-3490188">2023 年阅读节：银行假日狂欢的最佳时刻</a></strong></li></ul><p>现在，R&amp;L 宣布与 Just Vote 合作开展“Crash The Party”活动，说服 18-34 岁的人在 7 月 4 日星期四前往投票站。</p><p>经营雷丁和利兹的 Festival Republic 正在为登记投票的人提供免费门票作为竞赛奖品。</p><p> Festival Republic 董事总经理梅尔文·本 (Melvin Benn) 表示：“雷丁与利兹是全国最大的年轻人聚会之一，也是我们青年文化的核心。</p><p> “在将这些节日变成现实的过程中，我有幸亲眼目睹了下一代的活力和热情，在大选中听到他们的声音至关重要。”</p><p>他继续说道：“音乐产业一直是积极变革的重要力量，与 Just Vote 合作是一种很好的方式，可以让我们的观众在这个历史性时刻将他们的精力投入到行使民主权利中。” </p><figure id="attachment_3551954" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3551954" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3551954" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/ReadingandLeeds-festivals-2024-tickets-on-sale.jpg" alt="2023 年 8 月 27 日在英国雷丁里奇菲尔德大道举行的 2023 年雷丁节第 3 天烟花全景" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/ReadingandLeeds-festivals-2024-tickets-on-sale.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/ReadingandLeeds-festivals-2024-tickets-on-sale-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/ReadingandLeeds-festivals-2024-tickets-on-sale-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/ReadingandLeeds-festivals-2024-tickets-on-sale-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/ReadingandLeeds-festivals-2024-tickets-on-sale-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/ReadingandLeeds-festivals-2024-tickets-on-sale-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3551954" class="wp-caption-text"> 2023 年阅读节。图片来源：Joseph Okpako/WireImage/Getty</figcaption></figure><p>此外，<a href="https://www.nme.com/glastonbury-2024">格拉斯顿伯里音乐节</a>（在大选前一周举行）正在进行一场竞赛，以赢得今年活动的门票。它还将在现场举办互动式“Crash the Party”装置，提醒投注者前来投票。</p><p> Just Vote 创始人戴尔·文斯 (Dale Vince) 补充道：“我们感谢 Festival Republic、格拉斯顿伯里音乐节以及所有参与音乐节对 Just Vote 的大力支持。</p><p> “这是我们一生中最重要的大选，英国乐坛具有巨大的文化影响力，可以动员年轻人在 7 月 4 日发出自己的声音。”</p><p>他接着说：“我们还呼吁英国的音乐家利用你们的平台来召集年轻人登记，然后出去投票。参加这些音乐节的艺术家——如果您看到这种情况，请参与并提供帮助。”</p><p>有关该倡议的更多细节尚未公布。您可以在英国夏令时间 6 月 18 日星期二晚上 11:59 之前<a href="https://www.gov.uk/register-to-vote?step-by-step-nav=ff81c31c-3282-49df-85a4-013887130110#:~:text=Deadline%20for%20registering%20to%20vote,on%204%20July%202024." target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此登记投票</a>。</p><p> 2024 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节将由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dua-lipa">Dua Lipa</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/coldplay">Coldplay</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sza">SZA</a>领衔主演。本周早些时候，组织者透露了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-line-up-set-times-stage-splits-3749871">音乐节的完整阵容、舞台划分和时间安排</a>，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fans-react-as-full-glastonbury-2024-line-up-and-schedule-reveals-new-names-and-clashes-3762343">一些新名字</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/who-will-play-the-big-glastonbury-tba-secret-sets-fans-are-guessing-3762542">各种“TBA”秘密时段</a>。</p><p>与此同时， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/reading-leeds-2024-new-stage-chevron-video-photos-interview-2024-tickets-3587729">Melvin Benn 今年早些时候接受<em>NME</em>采访时谈到了 Reading &amp; Leeds 2024 年的“突破性”新舞台 The Chevron</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/reading-leeds-are-giving-away-tickets-to-encourage-young-people-to-vote-3763107">雷丁和利兹联队赠送门票以鼓励年轻人投票的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
